text: Shashikant Narsingrao Khedekar is Shiv Sena politician from Buldhana district, Maharashtra. He is a member of the 13th Maharashtra Legislative Assembly and represents the Sindkhed Raja Assembly Constituency. ==Positions held== * 2014: Elected to Maharashtra Legislative Assembly ==See also== * Buldhana Lok Sabha constituency ==References== ==External links== * Shiv Sena Official website Category:Members of the Maharashtra Legislative Assembly Category:Maharashtra MLAs 2014–2019 Category:Living people Category:Shiv Sena politicians Category:People from Buldhana district Category:Marathi politicians Category:1954 births
